rows.label: tlk41100141_01_msg0001
rows.name:
I used to live on an island, but it got
caught up in a conflict between Invidia
and Superbia.

rows.label: tlk41100141_01_msg0002
rows.name:
The grown-ups kept yelling at each
other about where to go, where the
best place for us would be.

rows.label: tlk41100141_01_msg0003
rows.name:
In the end, they split into two groups,
one for Invidia and one for Superbia,
and started fighting among themselves.

rows.label: tlk41100141_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Vandham said they
aren't all the same.

rows.label: tlk41100141_01_msg0006
rows.name: But frankly, I find that hard to believe...
